properties.areaDesc: Whitefish Bay (U.S. Portion)/Whitefish Point to Point Iroquois MI
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 4 at 4:09PM EST until January 6 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Gaylord MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Highest gusts up to 40 kt and highest waves around 11
feet expected.

* WHERE...Whitefish Bay (U. S. Portion)/Whitefish Point to Point
Iroquois MI.

* WHEN...From 11 PM Sunday to 10 AM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous highest waves
which could capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM SUNDAY TO 10 AM EST MONDAY
